ProcessName: This notable identifies instances where a PropertyList (.plist) file was created or modified in the ~/Library/LaunchAgents/ directory potentially indicating an attempt to achieve persistence on a macOS device by configuring a backdoor to launch at user login

UrlHostname: This query creates a Notable Event when a rare process Parent-Child relation invokes a (web) connection to a rare domain endpoint. This query serves to detect potential beacons as fast as possible without correlating on intervals and connection metrics
Techniques: notable0035: Connection from rare parent to child process to potential beaconing domain
